        <tr>
            <td style="height: 22px">
                <p style="text-align:center"><asp:Label ID="lblSentence15" runat="server" Text="Back pain is a debilitating condition that impacts the lives of millions of individuals every day. In fact, over 31 million Americans are susceptible to suffering from an episode of back pain at any given time. That&#8217;s at least 31 million lost moments spent playing with the kids or grandkids. 31 million days lost at work. 31 million rounds of golf, bicycle rides, and walks with the dog that will never be recovered, all due to excruciating pain that is forcing individuals to miss out on the things they love to do the most. Any number of activities, or even a lack of regular physical activity, can bring about a crippling episode, and that&#8217;s what makes treating back pain so difficult.  " Font-Bold="True"></asp:Label></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
